{"word":"συνάντομαι","slug":"συνάντομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνάντομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to fall in with, meet</i>, <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> or <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; in hostile sense, <i>to meet</i> in battle, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>φόρμιγγι ς.</el> <i>to approach</i> (<a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>use)</i> the lyre, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/>"}]}